text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text:
I cannot express…… 
how sorry I am about my last race!!

text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text:
That was not an honor roll student run! 
I must be a better role model!!

text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text:
Everyooooone!! Today, I'd like to show 
you all the class president's comeback 
kid ruuuun―!
